    <summary>Match-3 game for the terminal</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
          cmdjewel is a terminal match-3 game inspired by Bejeweled.
          Use the arrow keys and the spacebar (or Vim keybinds) to navigate, and match gems through space... in your terminal!
        </p>
